<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
	<title>夜夜—城市夜间电商</title>
	<style>
	html {
		font-size: 70px;
	}
	#qrcode {
  	  font-size: .2rem;
	}
	#qrcode .qrcode-first-part {
	  display: flex;
	  flex-direction: column;
	  align-items: center;
	  margin: .2rem;
	}
	#qrcode .qrcode-first-part img {
	  width: .68rem;
	  height: .68rem;
	  border-radius: 50%;
	}
	#qrcode .qrcode-first-part .logo-text {
	  font-size: .24rem;
	  padding: .1rem;
	  color: #232323;
	  font-weight: 600;
	}
	#qrcode .qrcode-first-part .text {
	  padding-top: .05rem;
	  font-size: .2rem;
	  color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
	}
	#qrcode .qrcode-second-part {
	  display: flex;
	  flex-direction: column;
	  align-items: center;
	  text-align: center;
	}
	#qrcode .first-text,
	#qrcode .second-text {
	  margin-top: .2rem;
	  line-height: .3rem;
	  color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
	}
	#qrcode .second-text {
	  margin: .1rem 0;
	}
	#qrcode #qrcode {
	  position: relative;
	  padding: 0 25%;
	  padding-bottom: .2rem;
	  width: 50%;
	}
	#qrcode .qrcode-third-part {
	  display: flex;
	  flex-direction: column;
	  align-items: center;
	  text-align: center;
	}
	#qrcode .download-button {
	  display: block;
	  color: #fff;
	  text-align: center;
	  text-decoration: none;
	  border-radius: 5px;
	  margin: .2rem;
	  position: relative;
	  font-size: .22rem;
	  background-color: #04BE02;
	  width: 80%;
	  padding: .1rem 0;
	  line-height: .3rem;
	}
	#qrcode .download-button:after {
	  content: " ";
	  width: 200%;
	  height: 200%;
	  position: absolute;
	  top: 0;
	  left: 0;
	  border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
	  border-radius: 10px;
	  transform: scale(0.5);
	  transform-origin: 0 0;
	  box-sizing: border-box;
	}
	#qrcode .download-button:active {
	  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
	  background-color: #039702;
	}
	#qrcode .ad-button {
	  font-size: .2rem;
	  margin-bottom: .2rem;
	  color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
	}
	.cross {
		width: 100%;
		height: .1rem;
		background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, .1);
	}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<section id="qrcode">
		<div class="qrcode-first-part">
			<img src="//cdn.yeyeapp.in/node-scheme/public/img/logo.png" alt="logo">
			<span class="logo-text">EveryCity EveryNight</span>
			<span class="text">专注夜间娱乐</span>
			<span class="text">派对交友，娱乐资讯，酒吧订台</span>			
		</div>
		<div class="cross"></div>
		<div class="qrcode-second-part">
			<span class="first-text">关注 &lceil; <strong>夜夜APP</strong>&rfloor; 实时查看好友有多懂你</span>
			<span class="second-text">长按识别，公众号：yeye_app</span>			
		</div>
		<img id="qrcode" src="http://7xotti.com2.z0.glb.qiniucdn.com/FmtkzlIy7340Mx7wRhI2fZMbBLow" alt="qrcode">
		<div class="cross"></div>
		<div class="qrcode-third-part">
			<a class="download-button" href="http://a.app.qq.com/o/simple.jsp?pkgname=in.yeyeapp">
				夜夜带你玩转夜生活 · 点击<strong>下载</strong>
			</a>			
		</div>
	</section>
</body>
</html>